      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable ride or a hands-on project? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current poor condition \u2014 it runs and drives, but shows considerable wear and will likely need some attention to get it back in great shape. If you're a DIY enthusiast or just need basic transportation on a tight budget, this could be the opportunity you've been waiting for! Come take a look and see if it's the right fit for you.",
