    {
      "id": "standard_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_2",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It has significant mechanical issues that make it unreliable for regular use, and it will require substantial repairs before it can be depended upon. The exterior shows considerable wear including noticeable rust, dents, and scratches. The interior is worn and shows signs of neglect. Best suited for someone prepared to invest in repairs or looking for parts.",
